high_descs: turn around and walk towards the kitchen stove
grab the pot off of the bottom right burner
turn around, walk a bit, and turn left to face the fridge
place the pot inside the fridge to cool, and then take it back out
turn around and walk forwards a bit, then turn right and walk towards the stove again
place the pot back on the bottom right burner
anns.task_desc: place a cooled pot on the bottom right burner

high_descs: Turn around and go to the stove.
Pick up the pot that is sitting on the front right burner.
Turn right and go to the refrigerator.
Place the pot on the top shelf inside the refrigerator for seven seconds before taking it back out.
Turn around and return to the stove.
Place the pot back on the front right burner.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pot on the stove.

high_descs: Pick up the large pot on the right of the stove.
Bring the pot to the fridge.
Chill the pot in the fridge.
Bring the pot to the stove.
Put the pot on the front right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pot on the front right of the stove.
